It's been a year since I challenged myself to live my life more fully and try
more new things.
我一年前挑戰自己要要多試試看新的東西為了有一個比較有趣的生活。
In that time I have, amongst too many other things to mention:
這一年以內做很多事，最重要的是我有：

 -Published a book 出版一本書
-Attended pride parade fo the first time. 參加同志遊行
-Ridden a cable car 坐纜車
-Tried face scraping 去挽臉
-Taught myself to make homemade alcohol.教自己怎麼做手工酒
-Done Movember 長一個月的鬍子
-Tried "something" in Amsterdam
-Tried all sorts of food and drink 嘗試各種各樣的食物跟飲料
-Tried an electric motorbike 試看看電動摩托車
-Visited Kending 去墾丁旅遊
-Grown a social media following of over 20000 people 得到超過2萬的粉絲

 
And in a few weeks I will launch my own clothes line. 然後幾個禮拜後會開始賣我自己設計的衣服.
I am so grateful to all of you for following me on this journey! 超感謝你們陪我一起過這個冒險！

 What new things did you try this year? 你這年以來有嘗試什麼新的東西呢？
